HtPqTy8s","ref":"Gen.10.5","text":"By these were the isles of the Gentiles divided in their lands; every one after his tongue, after their families, in their nations.","year":-2247},{"id":"recqF44bkCwjaQBYQ","ref":"Gen.10.6","text":"And the sons of Ham; Cush, and Mizraim, and Phut, and Canaan.","year":-2228},{"id":"rec4EZ9GPLgLT7cxF","ref":"Gen.10.7","text":"And the sons of Cush; Seba, and Havilah, and Sabtah, and Raamah, and Sabtecha: and the sons of Raamah; Sheba, and Dedan.","year":-2228},{"id":"recFnKypbUDlSKoyv","ref":"Gen.10.8","text":"And Cush begat Nimrod: he began to be a mighty one in the earth.","year":-2289}]}
